## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-102">사용 하 여 음성 플랫폼 신시사이저 인프라에 전송 되는 이벤트 종류를 정의 하는 사용자 지정 음성 합성 엔진을 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-102">Custom speech synthesis engines define the types of events submitted to the Speech platform synthesizer infrastructure with the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-103">사양 설정 하 여 수행 됩니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> 의 속성 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> 에 전달 된 인스턴스를 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> 구현 하는 클래스의 멤버를 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> 인터페이스에 전달를 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> 메서드는 사용자 지정 음성 엔진 구현의 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-103">Specification is performed by setting the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> property of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instances passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> member of the class implementing the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> method on a custom speech engine's implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-104">음성 플랫폼 인프라를 통해 현재 처리 하는 이벤트의 유형을 나타냅니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> 속성에는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> 말하기 구현에 전달 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-104">The Speech platform infrastructure indicates the type of events it is currently handling through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> passed to the speak implementation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-105">값 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> 는 비트 마스크 이며 여기서 멤버 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> 이벤트 형식에 해당 하는 비트의 위치를 정의 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-105">The value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> is a bitmask, where the members of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> define the location of the bit corresponding to the event type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-106">예를 들어 WordBoundary의 다섯 가지 (5)에서 반환한 값의 다섯 번째 비트를 의미 합니다.은 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> 사이트 이벤트 형식을 지 원하는 경우를 나타냅니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-106">For example, WordBoundary has a value of five (5), meaning the fifth bit in the value returned by <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> indicates if the site supports the event type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-107">아래 예제에서 상속 하는 사용자 지정 음성 합성 구현의 일부인 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, 및을 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, 및 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-107">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-108">구현 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-108">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-109">배열을 받습니다 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> 인스턴스 및 새 배열을 만듭니다 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> 전달 되는 인스턴스는 `Speak` 기본 합성 엔진에서 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-109">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
2.  <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-110">경우는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> 에서 열거형 값에서 찾을 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> 속성에는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> 반환한를 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> 의 각 속성 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> 인스턴스가 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, 구현</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-110">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> enumeration value by found from the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property of each <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> instance is <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, the implementation</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-111">읽을 텍스트의 Americanism Britishisms 변환 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-111">Translates Americanism to Britishisms in the text to be spoken.</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-112">경우는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> 속성에는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> 구현에 제공 하는 인터페이스 WordBoundary 이벤트 유형, 지원는 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> 인스턴스 이벤트 신시사이저 진행률 표시기가 만든 드라이브를 만드는 데 사용 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-112">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> interfaces provided to the implementation support the WordBoundary event type, a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instance is used to create an event to drive a synthesizer progress meter is created.</span></span>  
  
3.  <span data-ttu-id="dcfa8-113">이라고 하는 음성 렌더링 엔진이 수정 된 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> 배열입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dcfa8-113">A speech rendering engine is then called with the modified <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> array.</span></span>  
  
```  
private const int WordBoundaryFlag = 1 << (int)TtsEventId.WordBoundary;  
private readonly char[] spaces = new char[] { ' ', '\t', '\r', '\n' };  
internal struct UsVsUk  
{  
  internal string UK;  
  internal string US;  
}  
  
override public void Speak (TextFragment [] frags, IntPtr wfx, ITtsEngineSite site)  
{  
  TextFragment [] newFrags=new TextFragment[frags.Length];  
  
  for (int i=0;i<frags.Length;i++){  
    newFrags[i].State=frags[i].State;  
    //truncate  
    newFrags[i].TextToSpeak = frags[i].TextToSpeak.Substring(frags[i].TextOffset,  
                               frags[i].TextLength);  
    newFrags[i].TextLength = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Length;  
    newFrags[i].TextOffset = 0;  
    if (newFrags[i].State.Action == TtsEngineAction.Speak) {  
      //Us to UK conversion  
      foreach (UsVsUk term in TransList) {  
      newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Replace(term.US, term.UK);  
      }  
      //Generate progress meter events if supported  
      if ((site.EventInterest & WordBoundaryFlag) != 0) {  
      string[] subs = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Split(spaces);  
  
      foreach (string s in subs) {  
        int offset = newFrags[i].TextOffset;  
        SpeechEventInfo spEvent = new SpeechEventInfo((Int16)TtsEventId.WordBoundary,   
                (Int16)EventParameterType.Undefined,   
                 s.Length, new IntPtr(offset));  
        offset += s.Length;  
        if (s.Trim().Length > 0) {  
          SpeechEventInfo[] events = new SpeechEventInfo[1];  
          events[0] = spEvent;  
          site.AddEvents(events, 1);  
        }  
      }  
      }  
    }  
  }  
  
  _baseSynthesize.Speak(newFrags, wfx, site);  
  
}  
```
